{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444730/extras/GIF_Sizeok.gif?t=1737749318\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Halfway between a board game and a video game, Vanova's Stories is an investigative adventure for 2 to 4 players. Do you like wacky, colorful worlds, cooperating with your friends, and narrative point-and-clicks? Then this game is for you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444730/extras/EN_Angel.png?t=1737749318\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Discover fully hand-drawn settings and explore 7 of the 13 vibrant areas of the Undersee Hotel to uncover clues about the crime committed. Whether in 2D or 3D, your observational skills will be your greatest assets! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444730/extras/EN_Denis.png?t=1737749318\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This investigation site is inhabited by a cast of quirky and caricatured characters. In this demo, you\u2019ll have the chance to meet and question 3 of the 6 suspects. Some may refuse to talk to you... Perhaps your teammates will have better luck? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444730/extras/EN_Marc.png?t=1737749318\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Agility, intimidation, strength, charm\u2014everyone has their own unique ability that will lead them to clues only they can uncover. Your adventure and dialogue options will vary depending on your detective, so choose wisely!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444730/extras/EN_Stephanie.png?t=1737749318\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A suspect is refusing to talk to you, and you want to show him evidence to get him to confess? Swap clues with a teammate and get them to do it for you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444730/extras/EN_Claire.png?t=1737749318\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  Think you've discovered the truth? Get together with your friends and tell your boss what you've found, linking all the pieces together. Make sure everyone agrees, as a wrong hypothesis could cost you dearly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This is a demo version of the game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some pieces, characters, or clues are not yet unlocked. Discuss together to develop a theory, but keep in mind that there are still some unknowns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There may be some bugs present. If you find any, feel free to share them with us on our Discord server.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Important</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you're having trouble inviting one of your friends: Send a second invitation. Slow connections may cause some issues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444730/extras/EN_End.png?t=1737749318\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepage