atured characters. In this demo, you\u2019ll have the chance to meet and question 3 of the 6 suspects. Some may refuse to talk to you... Perhaps your teammates will have better luck? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444730/extras/EN_Marc.png?t=1737749318\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Agility, intimidation, strength, charm\u2014everyone has their own unique ability that will lead them to clues only they can uncover. Your adventure and dialogue options will vary depending on your detective, so choose wisely!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444730/extras/EN_Stephanie.png?t=1737749318\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A suspect is refusing to talk to you, and you want to show him evidence to get him to confess? Swap clues with a teammate and get them to do it for you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444730/extras/EN_Claire.png?t=1737749318\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  Think you've discovered the truth? Get together with your friends and tell your boss what you've found, linking all the pieces together. Make sure everyone agrees, as a wrong hypothesis could cost you dearly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This is a demo version of the game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some pieces, characters, or clues are not yet unlocked. Discuss together to develop a theory, but keep in mind that there are still some unknowns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragrap